modules.description: This module provides functions to serialize and deserialize MAC addresses to and from s-expressions, enabling seamless integration with ppx derivers for data serialization. It works with the `Macaddr.t` type, offering `sexp_of_t`, `t_of_sexp`, and `compare` functions. Use this module when persisting or transmitting MAC address data in s-expression format, such as in configuration files or network protocols.
